  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8 - \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Masked robbery in Ilawala - Two arrested",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two people have been arrested on charges related to the masked robbery incident involving house break-in and robbery in Ilawalai Police Division.",
        "A masked robber broke into a house near the Bandatharippu Behima Church early on Sunday morning, before opening the door of the house, four more masked robbers entered the house and threatened the house with knives and robbed them of 20 pounds of gold jewelry.",
        "While a complaint was lodged at the Ilawalai Police Station, the police, who conducted investigations, arrested two 20- and 21-year-olds based on the information provided by the family about the identities of the masked robbers.",
        "Ilawalai police said that the two arrested are drug addicts and further investigations are being conducted against them."
      ],
